title: Daciano Colbachini
text: Daciano Colbachini (31 October 1893 – 13 April 1982) was an Italian <a href="Hurdling">hurdler</a> who competed in the <a href="1912%20Summer%20Olympics">1912 Summer Olympics</a> and in the <a href="1920%20Summer%20Olympics">1920 Summer Olympics</a>. He was born in <a href="Padua">Padua</a>.
